These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, apple, pineapple, peas
1. the person eating watermelon is on the far left##1
2. the person eating apple is on the left or right of the person eating watermelon##3
3. the person eating apple is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Food   | watermelon | apple | pineapple | peas |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, milk, sprite, 7up
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | milk | mirinda | 7up | sprite |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, video-games, hiking, camping
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | writing | hiking | video-games | camping |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, western, zombie, time-travel
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
3. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | western | epic | time-travel | zombie |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, snowboarding, cricket, cycling
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Sport   | cycling | cricket | snowboarding | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-6::.
