.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-10::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, apple, spinach, raspberry
1. the person eating apple is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
2. the person eating apple is between the person eating pineapple and the person eating raspberry##2
3. the person eating pineapple is on the left or right of the person eating spinach##3
4. the person eating pineapple is on the left or right of the person eating spinach##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food   | raspberry | apple | pineapple | spinach |

