.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, salsa, d&b, soul
1. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of soul##1
2. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
3. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
4. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | salsa | house | soul |

 